The paper deals with the expressive power of description logic TBoxes, which is a topic that falls under the scope of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of semantic notions such as bisimulation and equisimulation suggests a connection to logic (cs.LO). The study of decision problems related to TBox rewriting involves database theory (cs.DB). The paper also mentions direct product, which is a concept in natural language processing (cs.CL). Finally, the lightweight DLs such as DL-Lite and EL are specific subfields of description logic (cs.DL).
